                        <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__prag"><add>consul</add></roleName></rs>,
                        <rs type="person" ref="pe__petrus_smelzer_QGW_II_I_1259">Petrus Smelzer <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__prag"><add>consul</add></roleName></rs>, <rs type="person" ref="pe__niklas_vroleich_QGW_II_I_1259">Nicolaus Frölich <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__prag"><add>consul</add></roleName></rs>, <rs type="person" ref="pe__frana_bischoff_QGW_II_I_1259">Frana Bischoff <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__prag"><add>consul</add></roleName></rs>, <rs type="person" ref="pe__niklas_gosler_QGW_II_I_1259">Johannes Gosler <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__prag"><add>consul</add></roleName></rs>, <rs type="person" ref="pe__christian_leitner_QGW_II_I_1180">Cristanus Leitner <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__prag"><add>consul</add></roleName></rs>, <rs type="person" ref="pe__johann_apotheker_QGW_II_I_1259">Johannes, <roleName type="prof">apothecarius</roleName>
                        <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__prag"><add>consul</add></roleName></rs>
                        <rs type="person" ref="pe__niklas_styr_QGW_II_I_1259">Nicolaus Styr de Leta Curia
                           <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__prag"><add>consul</add></roleName></rs>, <rs type="person" ref="pe__laurenz_martini_QGW_II_I_1259">Laurentius Martini <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__prag"><add>consul</add></roleName></rs> <rs type="person" ref="pe__pecha_sattler">Pecha, <roleName type="prof">frenifex</roleName></rs> <rs type="person" ref="pe__christian_helm_QGW_II_I_1259">Cristanus Holm <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__prag"><add>consul</add></roleName></rs>, <rs type="person" ref="pe__konrad_von_enns_QGW_II_I_1259">Conradus de Ens <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__prag"><add>consul</add></roleName></rs>, <rs type="person" ref="pe__pesslinus_salzer_QGW_II_I_1259">Pesslinus Salzer</rs>, <rs type="person" ref="pe__wenzel_uluschii_QGW_II_I_1259">Wenceslaus Vluschii <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__prag"><add>consul</add></roleName></rs>, <rs type="person" ref="pe__franz_hopfner_QGW_II_I_1180">Franciscus Hopfner <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__prag"><add>consul</add></roleName></rs>, <rs type="person" ref="pe__johann_chastner_QGW_II_I_1259">Henslinus Castner <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__prag"><add>consul</add></roleName></rs> et <rs type="person" ref="pe__albrecht_jurentem_QGW_II_I_1259">Albertus Jurentem <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__prag"><add>consul</add></roleName></rs>, <rs type="org" ref="org__prag">consules et iurati cives maioris civitatis
                        Pragensis</rs></rs>, <triggerstring n="disp">beurkunden</triggerstring>, dass ihr
                     <rs type="fn" role="recipient"><rs type="person" ref="pe__frana_hauer_QGW_II_I_1259"><roleName type="occ" corresp="org__prag">Mitbürger</roleName></rs>
                     Frana Hauer</rs> sein Haus, das früher dem Magister Bernhard gehört hatte,
                  gelegen in platea Czaltenariorum in acie ex opposito domus Theoderici de Ach ex
                  una et dotem plebani ecclesie beate Virginis ante Letam Curiam parte ex altera, et
                  penes domum Hanussconis Foit de Grecz ex una et Laurencii Enzinger parte ex alia ,
                  dem <rs type="fn" role="recipient"><rs type="person" ref="pe__georius_cham_QGW_II_I_1259">Georius de Kam ( coniurato nostro concivi in hereditate sua
                     Stopicz)</rs></rs>
                  <triggerstring n="disp">in Folge eines Tauschgeschäftes aufgelassen
                  habe</triggerstring>.</rs></p></div><div type="seal"><p><rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_I_1259"><rs type="fn" role="witness">Besiegelt mit
